{"tid":699705,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔Lulu幾個月練回22吋腰 一周三日主力做Pat Pat","createTime":"2018-06-12T17:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T07:18:25.000Z","uid":157545,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0dae388e61b119ad2925f28fab54a0f1b2e645b2","tid":699705,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T17:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1524240/org/a54defb3fa9acbcf573d376518d6197f.jpg/s4F1zlQyKjsp8byxHSxoUTCajAxOqIXDPFrLgDxay4A?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1524240%2Forg%2Fa54defb3fa9acbcf573d376518d6197f.jpg%2Fs4F1zlQyKjsp8byxHSxoUTCajAxOqIXDPFrLgDxay4A%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6b5559c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信好多人都知「大埔Lulu」董嘉儀最鍾意做運動，尤其是跑步，但不是每一位都知她曾經有段時間因為食得太多兼懶得郁動，搞到條腰去到26吋，成條腰唔見咗！不過，董嘉儀最近便在網上宣佈自己終於搵返條腰，更貼出一張度腰相，證明自己腰圍去返22.5吋，接近幾年前做Model時期的A4腰（22吋）：「雖然體重唔代表一切，但我都想健康同有個Fit啲嘅身型，經過大半年嘅運動同健康飲食，今日我終於有返條腰仔啦，22.5吋腰，繼續努力呀，下個目標係有線條。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1524241/org/6dd8a9577ade49d44546ec7bd4185fc5.jpg/817S17tHMVkw5onEnrAt0G4MkMmeXwduG1pXyxtaV8s?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1524241%2Forg%2F6dd8a9577ade49d44546ec7bd4185fc5.jpg%2F817S17tHMVkw5onEnrAt0G4MkMmeXwduG1pXyxtaV8s%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1cc02fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一星期三日運動　主力做Pat Pat操練<br />\n<br />\n其實要腰圍在大半年時間減走3.5吋（8.89厘米）並非易事，特別是起步點相當高的情況下。到底董嘉儀是如何減得咁快？她接受《香港01》訪問時便：「呢大半年我真係好乖，Keep住做帶氧運動同重力訓練，一星期至少三日做運動。」多以跑步消脂的她就指在重力訓練主要練Pat Pat：「因為下身瘦，上身自然都會瘦，好多人以為瘦腰最主要係做腹部運動，但教練就同我講做腿時會自然收緊腹部，都會練到個腹。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n水果蔬果不可少　食牛油果三文魚<br />\n<br />\n不怕練Pat Pat練到變歐美風格巨躉？董嘉儀笑謂：「我哋亞洲女仔好難練到咁，不過呢，個Pat Pat挺啲，望落個線條好睇啲，感覺對腳都長啲，着牛仔褲時會好靚！」那麼飲食方面有甚麼地方要注意？她答謂：「我早餐會食豐富啲，多數食牛油果、麵包同提子乾，再飲多杯豆漿。午餐都會食飯，清湯米粉比較多，多菜少肉。夜晚就食少少嘢，好似水果咁，好少食高澱粉質食物。」至於會唔會食時下最興的「超級食物」，董嘉儀答謂：「牛油果、三文魚嗰啲一定食。（亞麻籽同奇亞籽呢？）未試過呀，知道都好多人都話好飽肚。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1524288/org/1ffe0eb206f31cca2be72168acd32c2f.jpg/ObxPzbvuTUT2QaOr7PbPCLHYyvJ2CPglh10F6YddBek?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1524288%2Forg%2F1ffe0eb206f31cca2be72168acd32c2f.jpg%2FObxPzbvuTUT2QaOr7PbPCLHYyvJ2CPglh10F6YddBek%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2d3ffc3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d8ed5c93c7a0a1cc68be588a797538c717e00d1","tid":699705,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T18:02:57.000Z","msg":"對波大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d16d69426f54e19ba8a53cfe99908cee240f0e","tid":699705,"uid":54181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T18:17:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60ab643844d8d4b751c9848f9797e1f1771ba371","tid":699705,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d8ed5c93c7a0a1cc68be588a797538c717e00d1","tid":699705,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T18:02:57.000Z","msg":"對波大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T18:28:46.000Z","msg":"谷得超勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d5295d20f871d9fb060cefe82e1e39c54eca07","tid":699705,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T18:30:43.000Z","msg":"黑色肌膚給她的意義"},{"pid":"64c3113866eca2ec248aa3ea297b60c8f77ddfdb","tid":699705,"uid":134012,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T18:34:26.000Z","msg":"真人好瘦<br />\n黃美棋就真係大波啦"},{"pid":"3b35da703098dadf42f184083d7331c0598204f3","tid":699705,"uid":108266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T18:36:39.000Z","msg":"我ok bo"},{"pi